  "props": [
    {
      "type": "sign",
      "pos": [
        -2.5,
        0.0,
        2.5
      ],
      "rotation_y": 3.141592653589793,
      "message": "SPRAWL INDEX HALL\n\nAn alphabetised hall of header-scrolls. Each scroll declares the shape of one thing the Sprawl keeps. The shapes are dry. The shapes are dependable."
    },
    {
      "type": "sign",
      "pos": [
        2.5,
        0.0,
        2.5
      ],
      "rotation_y": 3.141592653589793,
      "message": "Pinned over the desk:\n\n'Look up before you reach. Reach before you ask. Ask before you guess. Guess only when the realm is on fire.'\n\n\u2014 posted by an Indexer who is no longer here."
    },
    {
      "type": "npc",
      "pos": [
        -0.5,
        0.0,
        0.5
      ],
      "rotation_y": 3.141592653589793,
      "name": "Indexer Yera",
      "body_color": [
        0.55,
        0.55,
        0.62,
        1.0
      ],
      "hat_color": [
        0.7,
        0.6,
        0.45,
        1.0
      ],
      "idle_hint": "[E] Speak with the indexer",
      "dialog_tree": {
        "start": "root",
        "nodes": {
          "root": {
            "speaker": "Indexer Yera",
            "text": "*she rubs her eyes. The candle is low. The desk is full of scrolls she has not got to today, and none she got to yesterday.*\n\nWalker. Yes. What are you looking for? I can find it. It will take a moment. It will probably take more than a moment.",
            "choices": [
              {
                "label": "Just looking.",
                "next": "look"
              },
              {
                "label": "How long have you been at this?",
                "next": "long"
              },
              {
                "label": "Walk well.",
                "next": "bye"
              }
            ]
          },
          "look": {
            "speaker": "Indexer Yera",
            "text": "Then look. There's a section on every shape the Sprawl knows. Most of them are correct. The ones that aren't, I will get to.\n\nIn the next breath, perhaps. Or the breath after.",
            "choices": [
              {
                "label": "Walk well.",
                "next": "bye"
              }
            ]
          },
          "long": {
            "speaker": "Indexer Yera",
            "text": "*she actually laughs.*\n\nLong enough that the answer doesn't help. Long enough that I have begun to remember the day I started, and the day I am supposed to finish, and the realm seems unconcerned about the difference between them.\n\nWalk well, walker. Don't take up indexing.",
            "choices": [
              {
                "label": "Walk well.",
                "next": "bye"
              }
            ]
          },
          "bye": {
            "speaker": "Indexer Yera",
            "text": "Walk well. Don't knock the scrolls."
          }
        }
      }
    }
  ],
